-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Bilfinger, Marks & Spencer, Deutsche Bank  
-- 
-- Wed May 21, 2014 12:01AM EDT
-- None



May 21 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Bilfinger and Marks & Spencer, on Wednesday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Bilfinger <GBFG.DE>: UBS raises target price to 86 euros from 84 euros; rating neutral  * Marks and Spencer <MKS.L>: Nomura raises target price to 560p from 520p; rating buyFollowing is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Wednesday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.   * Bilfinger <GBFG.DE>: UBS raises target price to 86 euros from 84 euros; rating neutral  * Deutsche Bank <DBKGn.DE>: Morgan Stanley cuts target price to 34 euros from 37 euros